title: Complete Badminton Training by Zhao Jianhua & Xiao Jie - Episode
description:
These are a great resource for people wishing to improve their badminton techniques, with good clear advice from two great teachers.

This is a repackage of episodes 16-30. Thanks and props to the original uploader.

I&#039;ve converted the .rmvb Real Media files to avis, and included all available English subtitle files - which (up to now) cover episodes 16-25.  

The recommended program for viewing is VLC which includes all codecs you&#039;ll need and a good subtitle viewer included.  You may wish to change your preferences in VLC to give the subtitles a yellow colour and a black outline, so they stand out against the white chinese subtitles hardcoded into the videos.

Also packaged is the torrent file for episodes 1-15 (avis and subs), in case anyone is missing it.

Any native speakers wishing to help out with the community of translators on the final 5 episodes should visit http://www.badmintoncentral.com/forums/showthread.php?t=48806
xt6666 will appreciate any help you can give.
